@startuml
title Domain-Aware PM Evaluation for Cloud SwiftSight

rectangle "Human Request" as Human
rectangle "PM Structuring" as PM
rectangle "Clarification Loop" as Clarify
rectangle "Child Work Items" as Work
rectangle "Review / QA Evidence" as Review

package "Cloud SwiftSight Domain" {
  rectangle "swiftsight-cloud\nBFF / Settings / Temporal / Registry" as Cloud
  rectangle "swiftsight-agent\nDICOM / Upload / SEND / PACS" as Agent
  rectangle "swiftcl\nWorkflow Match / DAG / Routing" as SwiftCL
  rectangle "swiftsight-worker\nModel Execution / Provenance" as Worker
}

Human --> PM : short feature request
PM --> Clarify : ask only missing info
Clarify --> PM : bounded answer
PM --> Work : project/lane split
Work --> Review : acceptance criteria\nreview evidence

PM ..> Cloud : settings/runtime context
PM ..> Agent : delivery / PACS context
PM ..> SwiftCL : workflow / routing context
PM ..> Worker : execution provenance context

note right of PM
Evaluate:
- correct project selection
- useful clarification
- executable work split
- domain risk awareness
- review/QA evidence
end note

@enduml
